bset.Subset\">⊆</a> <span class=\"fn\">y</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `x` is a subset of `y` and `y` is complete, then there is a completion of `x` which is also\na subset of `y`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/SuperSymmetry/SU5/ChargeSpectrum/Completions.html#SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum.exist_completions_subset_of_complete","kind":"theorem","line":308,"name":"SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum.exist_completions_subset_of_complete","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L308-L384"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/SuperSymmetry/SU5/ChargeSpectrum/Completions.html#SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum.self_subset_mem_completions\"><span class=\"name\">SuperSymmetry</span>.<span class=\"name\">SU5</span>.<span class=\"name\">ChargeSpectrum</span>.<span class=\"name\">self_subset_mem_completions</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#DecidableEq\">DecidableEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">S5 </span><span class=\"fn\">S10</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Finset/Defs.html#Finset\">Finset</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">y</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/SuperSymmetry/SU5/ChargeSpectrum/Basic.html#SuperSymmetry.SU5.ChargeSpectrum\">ChargeSpectrum</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝓩</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hy</span> : <span class=\"f